; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests auto-xact with a predicate that can't be handled by the
; quick matcher (post_pred), forcing fallback to regular eval.
; The expression "amount > 0" uses O_GT which post_pred doesn't handle,
; so it throws and the catch block falls back to regular evaluation.

= expr amount > 0
    Liabilities:Tax  (amount * 0.10)
    Assets:Tax       (-amount * 0.10)

2024/03/01 Test
    Expenses:Food     $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test bal
            $-110.00  Assets
            $-100.00    Checking
             $-10.00    Tax
             $100.00  Expenses:Food
              $10.00  Liabilities:Tax
--------------------
                   0
end test
